title: Readout of President Donald J. Trump’s Call with President Recep Tayyip Erdogan of Turkey – The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			

		Foreign Policy	

Issued on:
September 9, 2017
President Donald J. Trump spoke today with President Recep Tayyip Erdogan of Turkey.  President Trump emphasized the common commitment of the United States and Turkey to work together to increase regional stability.
